userdata.title: Hc vin k thut qun s
userdata.description: Hc vin K thut qun s c thnh lp theo Quyt nh s 146/CP ngy 08 thng 8 nm 1966 ca Hi ng Chnh ph vi tn gi ban u l Phn hiu II i hc Bch khoa. Ngy 28 thng 10 nm 1966, ti Hi trng ln i hc Bch khoa, B i hc v Trung hc chuyn nghip (nay l B Gio dc v o to) v B Quc phng long trng t chc L thnh lp Phn hiu II i hc Bch khoa, ng thi khai ging kho o to u tin. T , ngy 28 thng 10 nm 1966 c chn l Ngy truyn thng ca Hc vin K THUT QUN S. Ngy 13 thng 6 nm 1968, Th tng Chnh ph quyt nh i tn Phn hiu II i hc Bch khoa thnh trng i hc K THUT QUN S v ngy 15 thng 12 nm 1981, B Quc phng quyt nh thnh lp Hc vin K THUT QUN S trn c s trng i hc K THUT QUN S. Nhm pht huy tim nng tr tu ca i ng cc nh khoa hc, c s vt cht k thut hin i, cng tc qun l gio dc khoa hc, m rng hp tc quc t ca Hc vin K THUT QUN S v o to ngun nhn lc phc v s nghip cng nghip ha, hin i ha t nc, ngy 06 thng 6 nm 1991, Ch tch Hi ng B trng quyt nh cho php Hc vin mang thm tn i hc k thut L Qu n. Ngy 31 thng 1 nm 2008, Hc vin K THUT QUN S c Chnh ph quyt nh b sung vo danh sch cc trng i hc trng im quc gia. Hin nay, Hc vin K THUT QUN S bin ch gm c: Ban Gim c v 49 c quan, n v trc thuc.
